  "markdown": "![](/images/NewsPageTitle.png)\n\n# **UPCOMING EVENTS**\n\n## Ocean Best Practices Workshop VIII\n\n14-18 October 2024, Virtual | <https://www.oceanbestpractices.org/ocean-best-practices-systems/news-and-events/workshop/workshop-viii/>\n\n## One Ocean Science Congress\n\n4-6 June 2025, Nice, France | <https://one-ocean-science-2025.org/>\n\n## 2025 UN Ocean Conference\n\n9-13 June 2025, Nice, France | <https://sdgs.un.org/conferences/ocean2025>\n\nIf you are aware of other conferences or events that are relevant to the Marine Life 2030 community, please email them to [[email protected]](/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#620f03100b0c070e0b04075052515222050f030b0e4c010d0f).",
